ive; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Linear models for classification: decision boundary\"\n        title=\"Linear models for classification: decision boundary\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/15ec7/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/9ac50/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg 173w,\n/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/8d48c/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg 345w,\n/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/15ec7/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg 690w,\n/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/af659/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg 1035w,\n/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/89b2d/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg 1380w,\n/blog/static/cd65e1dac411dece567fcb551f262848/c06f5/linear_models_for_clf_2.jpg 1668w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Linear models for classification: decision boundary</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"other-readings\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#other-readings\" aria-label=\"other readings permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Other readings</h2>\n<p>I also managed to pick up on <a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/Math-Gene-Keith-Devlin/dp/0465016197\">The Math Gene</a>. I found it while looking for good sources for theoretical ML books. This book investigates the development of mathematical aptitude in human beings. Interestingly enough, the claim is the ability to comprehend language is also the same that allows mathematical thinking as well.</p>\n<p><em>fin</em>.</p>","timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"I covered my plans around a study break in a previous post, concluded on 1st Jan 2021. My experience was highly positive, a quick set of…","frontmatter":{"title":"After effects of a study break","cover":"https://picsum.photos/seed/seed_n/1500/300","date":"2020-12-27T00:00:00.000Z","categories":["readings"],"tags":["machine learning","programming"]},"fields":{"slug":"/after-effects-of-a-study-break","date":"December 26, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/after-effects-of-a-study-break","nexttitle":"Study Breaks","nextslug":"/study-breaks","prevtitle":"Building a linked list in rust","prevslug":"/building-a-linked-list-in-rust"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3969716136"]}